---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'Privacy Policy | Ads Calculator';
const description = 'Privacy Policy of Ads Calculator. Learn how we handle your data, cookies, and compliance with GDPR, CCPA, and Google AdSense policies.';
const keywords = 'privacy policy, ads calculator privacy, data compliance, gdpr compliance, adsense privacy policy';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} keywords={keywords} lang="en">
  <main class="flex-grow py-12 sm:py-20 px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white/80 dark:bg-slate-900/80 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-[2rem] shadow-2xl border border-white/20 dark:border-white/5 p-8 sm:p-12 animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-4 duration-1000">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2 tracking-tight">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm mb-10">Last updated: June 2026</p>

      <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">1. Information About the Site Operator</h2>
          <p>The website <strong>adsroicalc.com</strong> (hereinafter referred to as the "Site" or "Ads Calculator") is operated by <strong>PauApps</strong>. We are dedicated to providing marketing professionals, growth marketers, and business owners with accurate calculation tools for Return on Ad Spend (ROAS), Return on Investment (ROI), cost-per-acquisition (CPA), and breakeven performance points.</p>
          <p>For any enquiries regarding this Privacy Policy or how your data is handled, you can reach out directly via email: <a href="mailto:info@adsroicalc.com" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">info@adsroicalc.com</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">2. No Direct Data Collection</h2>
          <p>At Ads Calculator, your privacy is paramount. <strong>We do not collect, store, or transmit any data that you enter into our calculation tools.</strong> All calculations are executed locally and directly within your web browser (client-side). None of your financial, product cost, ad spend, or revenue inputs are sent to our servers or stored by us.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">3. Third-Party Services and Analytics</h2>
          <p>While we do not collect personal data directly, we use third-party services that set cookies and gather anonymous usage statistics to help us monitor performance, improve user experience, and fund our operations:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Google Analytics 4 (GA4):</strong> We use GA4 to compile anonymous statistics about visits, pages viewed, user devices, and general geographic location. It does not record personally identifiable information (PII).</li>
            <li><strong>Google Tag Manager (GTM):</strong> Used to safely deploy and manage code snippets and scripts on our Site.</li>
            <li><strong>Google AdSense:</strong> We display advertisements served by Google AdSense to generate revenue to maintain this free resource. Google AdSense uses cookies to deliver relevant ads based on your preferences and browsing history.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">4. Google AdSense & Personalized Advertising Disclosure</h2>
          <p>Google AdSense is a third-party vendor that uses cookies to serve ads on our Site. Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads to our users based on their visits to this Site and/or other sites on the Internet.</p>
          <p>Users may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting Google's ad settings:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>To manage your personalized ad settings, visit: <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">Google Ads Settings</a></li>
            <li>Alternatively, you can opt out of a third-party vendor's use of cookies for personalized advertising by visiting: <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">About Ads Choices</a></li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">5. Cookie Policy</h2>
          <p>We use both first-party and third-party cookies for site functionality, analytics, and advertising. For a complete list of cookies, their purposes, and how to manage or disable them, please consult our dedicated <a href="/cookies" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">Cookie Policy</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">6. User Rights (GDPR & CCPA Compliance)</h2>
          <p>Depending on your location, you may have specific data protection rights under regulations like the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) for EEA residents, and the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA) for California residents:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>GDPR (EEA):</strong> You have the right to access, rectify, or erase any anonymous logs associated with your IP address, or object to processing. Because we do not store PII, we have no identifiable records, but you can exercise your rights by contacting <a href="mailto:info@adsroicalc.com" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">info@adsroicalc.com</a>.</li>
            <li><strong>CCPA/CPRA (California):</strong> You have the right to request disclosure of what personal information is collected/sold and opt out of the sale or sharing of your personal info. As mentioned, we do not collect personal data directly; Google AdSense personalized ads can be opted out using the settings mentioned in Section 4.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">7. Policy Updates</h2>
          <p>We reserve the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Changes will be posted immediately on this page with an updated date. Your continued use of the Site following updates constitutes your formal acceptance of the modified terms.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
